{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782405947591,"sessionID":"ses_10053ce1fffeJEFUjEAeuZr4YW","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4h6EgRkvTKlVpIBWjMlD2H1F","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\harmonyos-cangjie-translation-checklist.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\harmonyos-cangjie-translation-checklist.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # HarmonyOS Cangjie Translation Checklist\n2: \n3: 面向 Android Java app 迁移到 HarmonyOS Cangjie 的阶段性检查表。它来自 Spendee 案例记录和后续构建修复经验，目标是在每个 `opencode-cj` phase 结束时先抓住高频编译/宏展开问题，再进入下一阶段。\n4: \n5: ## 使用时机\n6: \n7: 1. 每个翻译 phase 开始前，把本 phase 可能触及的条目加入 `opencode-cj` prompt。\n8: 2. 每个 phase 结束后，先运行完整构建门禁：\n9: \n10:    `<python>` 表示当前 Python 解释器：macOS/Linux 可用 `python3`，Windows 可用 `py -3` 或 `python`。\n11: \n12:    ```bash\n13:    <python> scripts/shared/reports/build_hap_report.py \\\n14:      --workspace-root <translation-workspace> \\\n15:      --target-project <target-project> \\\n16:      --phase <phase-name>\n17:    ```\n18: \n19: 3. 如果报告失败，把 `build-reports/<phase-name>/build-report.md` 和首个 blocker 交给 `opencode-cj` 修复当前 phase，不要先开启下一阶段。\n20: 4. 构建通过后，再进入运行时 smoke 或行为验证。\n21: \n22: ## 资源和字符串边界\n23: \n24: - 不要把 `@r(...)` / `AppResource` 直接当作普通 `String`。\n25: - UI prop 如果可能接收资源字符串，优先使用 `ResourceStr`，或在边界处做 SDK 支持的显式转换。\n26: - 不要对 `ResourceStr` 调用普通字符串方法，例如 `isEmpty()`；需要空态时使用独立 `Bool` 状态。\n27: - 迁移 Android `setText(...)` 时，确认 HarmonyOS 端有明确的状态赋值或可观察数据源驱动文本刷新。\n28: - 每次资源迁移后，检查 `string.json`、media 资源和实际 UI 引用，避免保留旧 placeholder key 或缺失 AppScope/entry 双层资源。\n29: \n30: ## Option 和控制流\n31: \n32: - 不要生成 Java/Kotlin 风格的 `Option.get()`。\n33: - 非 UI helper 中使用 `match`、显式 `case Some(...)` / `case None`，或当前 SDK 支持的安全访问 API。\n34: - UI 构建逻辑中避免直接让 `match` 分支裸露生成不兼容的 component 形态；需要时拆成命名 `@Builder`。\n35: - 启动/依赖注入状态建议拆成明确的 `Bool`、错误资源、服务 option 解包 helper，减少 `@Component` 宏失败面。\n36: \n37: ## 包结构和导入\n38: \n39: - 避免 root package 与 `pages` / `routing` 之间出现环形依赖。公共 route 类型优先放在 `routing` 或独立 models/helpers 包。\n40: - UI 文件中避免宽泛 `std.collection.*` 导入；它可能和 ArkUI 组件名冲突，例如 `Stack`。\n41: - 需要集合类型时优先显式导入或限定命名。\n42: - helper 类型如果会通过 public `@Component` 生成构造器暴露，确认类型本身也是必要的 public 可见性。\n43: - 不要把临时 template/cache 文件当成迁移输入；`.cache`、build output 和 diagnostic log 只作为诊断证据。\n44: \n45: ## ArkUI Component 和 Builder\n46: \n47: - `@BuilderParam` 优先传入命名 `@Builder` 方法，不要依赖未验证的 inline closure 或 trailing component block。\n48: - 自定义容器组件要按当前 SDK 支持的构造器/slot 形态实现，不能照搬 ArkTS 示例。\n49: - 校验 ArkUI named arguments 和 modifiers 来自当前 Cangjie HarmonyOS SDK 文档，而不是只参考 ArkTS。\n50: - 对 `@Component` macro 失败，先缩小到入口组件状态、构造器 public 类型、资源字符串类型和 `@Publish` 字段类型这四类高频根因。\n51: - 组件内部紧密相关的 owner state 文本可直接在 owning page builder 中渲染，避免子组件 prop 复用导致同会话文本不刷新。\n52: \n53: ## 状态和可观察集合\n54: \n55: - 路由和跨页面状态模型使用 SDK 支持的 `@Observed`、`@Publish` 和明确字段类型。\n56: - 需要列表变化驱动 UI 时，使用 `ObservedArrayList` 等 SDK 支持的数据源，并给 `ForEach` 提供稳定 key。\n57: - 不要假设 `ObservedArrayList` 是普通 iterator；辅助逻辑中用下标访问或 SDK 支持方法。\n58: - 跨组件变化的 prop 需要 `@Prop` / `@Link` / `@Watch` 等明确同步链路。\n59: - 对 primitive totals、余额、计数等关键展示值，保存/编辑/删除成功后优先执行明确赋值，避免只依赖持久化回读触发 UI。\n60: \n61: ## 测试迁移和验证\n62: \n63: - 源项目已有测试时，当前 phase 相关测试应迁移或改写为目标侧测试，验证翻译后的业务、数据、状态、资源或刷新行为。\n64: - 源项目没有测试时，应为核心可测试逻辑补充适量测试；源测试过少时，应优先补高风险行为测试。\n65: - 如果当前 SDK/模板不支持某类自动化测试，应保持代码可测试，并记录 deferred validation、替代验证方法和后续完成路径。\n66: - 不要为了通过构建直接删除、禁用或弱化已迁移/生成的测试；应修实现、修测试集成，或明确记录当前阶段测试限制。\n67: \n68: ## 构建配置和工具链\n69: \n70: - 完整 HAP 构建必须使用 DevEco Cangjie plugin 管理的 full SDK，例如 `~/.cangjie-sdk/<version>/cangjie`；standalone `~/.local/cangjie` 只能代表轻量 `cjc` / `cjpm` 可用。\n71: - 缺少 full SDK 时，应先安装/启用 DevEco Studio Cangjie plugin，再继续 full build gate。\n72: - 每阶段记录构建命令、失败阶段、首个 blocker 和已解决 blocker。\n73: - 常见阶段含义：\n74:   - `ohpm install`：依赖、registry、模板测试依赖或 oh-package 问题。\n75:   - `SyncCangjieResource`：资源生成、配置 schema、Cangjie build support 注入问题。\n76:   - `CompileCangjie`：Cangjie 语法、宏展开、包依赖、ArkUI API 问题。\n77:   - `PackageHap`：资源/loader/package 产物问题。\n78:   - `SignHap`：签名配置问题；未签名 debug HAP 通常可能只是 warning。\n79: - full build 通过前，不要把 standalone `cjpm check` 失败简单等同于 HAP 构建失败；两者依赖来源不同。\n80: \n81: ## opencode-cj 修复交接\n82: \n83: - `apply_patch` 失败后必须 read-back，因为失败可能部分落盘。\n84: - `L.map is not a function`、`apply_patch verification failed`、`Failed to read file to update` 要分开记录。\n85: - 长 phase 被打断或恢复时，先让 `opencode-cj` 检查文件系统当前状态，再继续，不要重复生成同名组件或服务。\n86: - 构建 blocker prompt 应包含：\n87:   - 当前 phase 名称。\n88:   - `build-report.md` 路径。\n89:   - 失败阶段。\n90:   - 首个 blocker message 和 location。\n91:   - 只修当前 phase blocker 的约束。\n92: \n93: ## Phase Gate 验收\n94: \n95: - `build_hap_report.py` 的 Markdown/JSON 报告存在。\n96: - 报告包含 command、result、failed stage、first blocker、warnings、HAP artifacts。\n97: - 如果失败，已有 `opencode-build-blocker-prompt.txt` 可直接交给 `opencode-cj`。\n98: - 如果成功，报告记录 full build gate 通过，且可把本 phase 的已知编译 blocker 标为 resolved。\n99: - 下一 phase 只能在构建通过，或用户明确批准带 blocker 继续时开始。\n100: \n101: ## Spendee 证据映射\n102: \n103: - `@r(...)` / `ResourceStr` 误用导致重复 generic inference 和 macro blocker。\n104: - `Option.get()` 在当前 SDK 下不可用，入口和服务解包需改为显式 `match`。\n105: - root/pages/routing 包循环会阻断 `CompileCangjie`。\n106: - UI 文件中的 `std.collection.*` 与 ArkUI `Stack` 名称冲突。\n107: - `@BuilderParam` 命名 builder 比 inline closure 更稳定。\n108: - `ObservedArrayList` 不能按普通 `for-in` 假设处理。\n109: - 同会话 finance totals 刷新最终需要 owner state、显式赋值和可观察列表配合，构建通过不能替代运行时刷新验证。\n110: - 如果 full SDK 在 Phase 1 就接入，许多 Cangjie/ArkUI 编译问题可以在引入当 phase 就暴露，而不是累积到最终构建。\n\n(End of file - total 110 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# HarmonyOS Cangjie Translation Checklist\n\n面向 Android Java app 迁移到 HarmonyOS Cangjie 的阶段性检查表。它来自 Spendee 案例记录和后续构建修复经验，目标是在每个 `opencode-cj` phase 结束时先抓住高频编译/宏展开问题，再进入下一阶段。\n\n## 使用时机\n\n1. 每个翻译 phase 开始前，把本 phase 可能触及的条目加入 `opencode-cj` prompt。\n2. 每个 phase 结束后，先运行完整构建门禁：\n\n   `<python>` 表示当前 Python 解释器：macOS/Linux 可用 `python3`，Windows 可用 `py -3` 或 `python`。\n\n   ```bash\n   <python> scripts/shared/reports/build_hap_report.py \\\n     --workspace-root <translation-workspace> \\\n     --target-project <target-project> \\\n     --phase <phase-name>\n   ```\n\n3. 如果报告失败，把 `build-reports/<phase-name>/build-report.md` 和首个 blocker 交给 `opencode-cj` 修复当前 phase，不要先开启下一阶段。\n4. 构建通过后，再进入运行时 smoke 或行为验证。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"..\\..\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\harmonyos-cangjie-translation-checklist.md","time":{"start":1782405947580,"end":1782405947589}},"id":"prt_effac60a9001zEOMQB5AHPmQ5h","sessionID":"ses_10053ce1fffeJEFUjEAeuZr4YW","messageID":"msg_effac4a4d0015i3pjScJYHFDRw"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782405947643,"sessionID":"ses_10053ce1fffeJEFUjEAeuZr4YW","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_JE87QMKlaBMST4ppS381zjgs","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-coverage-gates\\phase-04-home-history-discovery.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-coverage-gates\\phase-04-home-history-discovery.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Phase Coverage Gate Report\n2: \n3: - Phase: `phase-04-home-history-discovery`\n4: \n5: ## Goal\n6: \n7: Validate that the current implementation phase can close. Every current-phase critical/high source feature must be implemented, platform-replaced, marked not-applicable with evidence, or explicitly deferred with complete blocker/fallback/risk/future-path evidence. Implemented/replaced items also need sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence.\n8: \n9: ## Summary\n10: \n11: | metric | value |\n12: | --- | --- |\n13: | phaseEntries | 30 |\n14: | phaseCriticalHighEntries | 26 |\n15: | openCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n16: | invalidStatusCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n17: | deferredCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n18: | simplifiedCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n19: | simplifiedCriticalHighRatio | 0.0 |\n20: | simplifiedWithoutReasonCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n21: | simplifiedWithoutEndpointOrTestCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n22: | incompleteDeferredCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n23: | weakDeferredJustificationCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n24: | genericDeferredTextCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n25: | repeatedDeferredJustificationGroups | 0 |\n26: | repeatedImplementedEvidenceGroups | 0 |\n27: | repeatedImplementedEndpointGroups | 0 |\n28: | broadImplementedEndpointCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n29: | unverifiedTestEvidenceCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n30: | testEvidenceVerifiedByLatestTestGateEntries | 0 |\n31: | weakEvidenceCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n32: | implementedWithoutEndpointOrTestCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n33: | missingSourceBehaviorCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n34: | missingTargetBehaviorCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n35: | missingVerificationEvidenceCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n36: | parityMismatchCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n37: | allowedParityLevels | ['', 'deferred', 'equivalent', 'not-applicable', 'platform-replaced', 'simplified', 'unverified'] |\n38: | deferredRequiredFields | ['sourceEvidence', 'deferredReason', 'targetFallback', 'risk', 'futureCompletionPath'] |\n39: | openCriticalHighPlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n40: | mustCompletePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n41: | needsEvidencePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |\n42: \n43: ## Status Counts\n44: \n45: | status | count |\n46: | --- | --- |\n47: | implemented | 18 |\n48: | not-applicable | 12 |\n49: \n50: ## Test Build Evidence\n51: \n52: | metric | value |\n53: | --- | --- |\n54: | acceptedPass | False |\n55: | acceptedReport |  |\n56: | acceptedPhase |  |\n57: | latestResult | TEST_COMPILE_FAIL |\n58: | latestReport | D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\test-build-reports\\phase-03-onboarding-login-profile\\test-build-report.md |\n59: \n60: ## Findings\n61: \n62: _No phase gate findings._\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Phase Coverage Gate Report\n\n- Phase: `phase-04-home-history-discovery`\n\n## Goal\n\nValidate that the current implementation phase can close. Every current-phase critical/high source feature must be implemented, platform-replaced, marked not-applicable with evidence, or explicitly deferred with complete blocker/fallback/risk/future-path evidence. Implemented/replaced items also need sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence.\n\n## Summary\n\n| metric | value |\n| --- | --- |\n| phaseEntries | 30 |\n| phaseCriticalHighEntries | 26 |\n| openCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n| invalidStatusCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n| deferredCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n| simplifiedCriticalHighEntries | 0 |\n| simplifiedCriticalHighRatio | 0.0 |\n| simplifiedWithoutReasonCriticalHighEntries | 0 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"translation-inputs\\phase-coverage-gates\\phase-04-home-history-discovery.md","time":{"start":1782405947633,"end":1782405947642}},"id":"prt_effac60bf001wRkcT2A5i1NmR3","sessionID":"ses_10053ce1fffeJEFUjEAeuZr4YW","messageID":"msg_effac4a4d0015i3pjScJYHFDRw"}}
